---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Hailang Dam (VPHEP) — CP Systems" description="Restoration of gate groove area of diversion tunnel at Vishnugadh Pipalkoti Hydroelectric Project in two phases.">
  <Header />

  <div class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="page-header__title">Hailang Dam (VPHEP)</h1>
      <div class="page-header__breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a> <span>/</span> <a href="#">Projects</a> <span>/</span> <span>Hailang Dam</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Overview -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-block animate-on-scroll">
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Dam Restoration</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Vishnugadh Pipalkoti Hydroelectric Project</h2>
          <p>
            Restoration of the damaged portion in the gate groove area of the Diversion Tunnel at the under-construction VPHEP (444 MW) on Bhagirathi River, District Chamoli (Uttarakhand). The dam site is located near Helang. Work executed in two distinct phases during lean season.
          </p>
          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; margin-top: 20px;">
            <div style="background: var(--beige); padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px;">
              <strong style="color: var(--navy); font-size: 0.85rem;">Client</strong><br/>
              <span>THDCIL</span>
            </div>
            <div style="background: var(--beige); padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px;">
              <strong style="color: var(--navy); font-size: 0.85rem;">Location</strong><br/>
              <span>Helang, Chamoli, Uttarakhand</span>
            </div>
            <div style="background: var(--beige); padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px;">
              <strong style="color: var(--navy); font-size: 0.85rem;">Capacity</strong><br/>
              <span>444 MW on Bhagirathi River</span>
            </div>
            <div style="background: var(--beige); padding: 16px; border-radius: 8px;">
              <strong style="color: var(--navy); font-size: 0.85rem;">DT Discharge</strong><br/>
              <span>50-60 Cumec during lean season</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content-block__image">
          <img src="/images/pdf_page_21_img_145.jpg" alt="Hailang Dam VPHEP" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Salient Features -->
  <section class="section section--beige">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Project Details</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">Salient Features & Scope</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 24px;">Two gates provided in the 10.50m × 10.50m box-type portion of the Diversion Tunnel at a distance of ~16m from the DT portal and ~50m from the DT intake. The repair of gate's groove, pier and side walls executed in phasing — Phase 1 for right side gate & Phase 2 for left side gate.</p>
      <div class="grid grid--2">
        <ul class="scope-list">
          <li>Removal of debris from top slab of DT</li>
          <li>Cutting of DT top slab by Diamond wire saw cutter</li>
          <li>Coffer dam with boulder-filled MS boxes in 50-60 cumec flow</li>
          <li>Lowering MS boxes by crane into flowing Alaknanda River</li>
          <li>Scaling & removing loose concrete by breaker</li>
          <li>Drilling, anchoring & fixing new reinforcement steel</li>
        </ul>
        <ul class="scope-list">
          <li>Pouring Micro Concrete above & under water</li>
          <li>Sealing cracks, honeycomb with Epoxy Putty</li>
          <li>Concrete surface repair with Epoxy Mortar</li>
          <li>3-component Epoxy grout in gate groove & T guide plate</li>
          <li>Removal of boulder-filled MS boxes</li>
          <li>Fabrication & fixing of MS cover plate over slab cutting</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Phase 1: Right Side Gate -->
  <section class="section" id="phase1">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="phase-header">
        <span class="phase-badge">Phase 1 — Right Side Gate</span>
        <span class="phase-period">January 2024 — March 2024</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Repair of Right Bay & Gate Groove</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 24px;">Phase 1 focused on the right side gate repair during lean season (Jan–Mar 2024). Operations included cutting the DT slab for access, making temporary diversion inside the tunnel, and complete reconstruction of the pier and side walls.</p>
      <div class="grid grid--3" style="margin-top: 20px;">
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/slide_8_img_1.jpg" alt="Debris Removal" /><span class="gallery-caption">Removal of debris from DT</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/slide_8_img_2.jpg" alt="Marking for Cutting" /><span class="gallery-caption">Marking for DT slab cutting</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/slide_10_img_1.jpg" alt="Opening Made" /><span class="gallery-caption">Opening made by cutting DT slab</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/slide_11_img_1.jpg" alt="Damage Inside DT" /><span class="gallery-caption">Damages inside diversion tunnel</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/slide_12_img_1.jpg" alt="Temporary Diversion" /><span class="gallery-caption">Temporary diversion for right bay repair</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/slide_14_img_1.jpg" alt="Reinforcement & Concreting" /><span class="gallery-caption">Reinforcement & concreting through hopper</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/slide_14_img_2.jpg" alt="Pier Repair" /><span class="gallery-caption">Pier reinforcement fixing</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/slide_15_img_2.jpg" alt="Concreting" /><span class="gallery-caption">Concreting through hopper & pipe</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/slide_16_img_1.jpg" alt="Repaired Gate Groove" /><span class="gallery-caption">Completed — Repaired gate groove</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Phase 2: Left Side Gate -->
  <section class="section section--beige" id="phase2">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="phase-header">
        <span class="phase-badge phase-badge--2">Phase 2 — Left Side Gate</span>
        <span class="phase-period">December 2024 — March 2025</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="section-title">Repair of Left Bay & Gate Groove</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 24px;">Phase 2 focused on the left side gate repair during the next lean season (Dec 2024 – Mar 2025). Involved cutting the left side DT slab for approach, making temporary diversion, rebaring in damaged portions of the left side wall, and underwater micro concrete pouring.</p>
      <div class="grid grid--3" style="margin-top: 20px;">
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/slide_18_img_1.jpg" alt="Left Side Slab Cutting" /><span class="gallery-caption">Left side DT slab cutting for approach</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/slide_18_img_2.jpg" alt="Slab Access" /><span class="gallery-caption">Making approach to damaged area</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/slide_19_img_1.jpg" alt="THDC Inspection" /><span class="gallery-caption">Inspection by THDC & temporary diversion</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/slide_19_img_2.jpg" alt="Diversion Inside DT" /><span class="gallery-caption">Temporary diversion inside tunnel</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/slide_20_img_1.jpg" alt="Rebaring" /><span class="gallery-caption">Rebaring in damaged left side wall</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/slide_21_img_1.jpg" alt="Underwater Concrete" /><span class="gallery-caption">Pouring underwater micro concrete</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/slide_22_img_1.jpg" alt="MS Slab Cover" /><span class="gallery-caption">Fabricating MS DT slab cover</span></div>
        <div class="gallery-item"><img src="/images/slide_22_img_2.jpg" alt="Slab Cover Placed" /><span class="gallery-caption">Placing slab cover over cut portion</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .gallery-item { border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden; position: relative; box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); }
  .gallery-item img { width: 100%; height: 240px; object-fit: cover; transition: transform 0.4s ease; }
  .gallery-item:hover img { transform: scale(1.05); }
  .gallery-caption {
    display: block; padding: 8px 12px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--grey-text);
    text-align: center; background: var(--white); font-weight: 500;
  }
  .phase-header {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .phase-badge {
    display: inline-block; background: var(--navy); color: var(--gold); padding: 6px 20px;
    border-radius: 50px; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  .phase-badge--2 { background: var(--gold); color: var(--navy); }
  .phase-period {
    font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--grey-text); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }
</style>
